description:
FEMICOIN was developed to solve the issues involving feminism under the concept of ‘Equality’ and ‘ Humanism’.
We intend to serve the society by launching services and items contributing to feminism through blockchain so that the public could receive them easily.

FEMICOIN will be purchasable like a real commodity in the FEMICOIN Platform. It is a ‘Mining Platform’ which has solved the existing weaknesses of mining coins by providing benefits for holders continuously.

The usage of FEMI COIN are as follows.

1) Signature items in FEMICOIN Platform are purchasable by FEMICOIN only.
2) Proceeds from the platform will be shared among FEMICOIN holders.
3) If you hold a large amount of FEMICOIN long term, you will be given the right to purchase special items in advance.

If you buy items in the FEMICOIN Platform by Proof of Purchasing, FEMICOIN will be distributed in accordance with the level of contribution.
name: Femicoin
